cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY

The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for detecting clickbaits in online content. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) techniques. Additionally, the paper deals with the ethical implications of clickbaits, which could fall under the sub-category of cs.CY (Computers and Society).
